"   <h1>",
"    REFERENCES",
"   </h1>",
"   <ol id=\"reference\">",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?24/12/24778/abstract/1\">",
"      A piece of my mind. It's over, Debbie. JAMA 1988; 259:272.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     Kass, L. Neither for love nor money: why doctors must not kill. Public Interest 1989; No.",
"    </li>",
